Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier  而那也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.27,0:00:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.47,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同时站在火线的两端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.15,0:00:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绕过危险的转角  追过生与死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.62,0:00:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑战谎言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.52,0:00:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论编织出多少谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.26,0:00:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相还是会照出光明的轮廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.21,0:00:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.74,0:00:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.31,0:00:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当我们的痛苦都抛在脑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.68,0:00:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.25,0:00:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是士兵不是站着就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.82,0:01:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它们留给审判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.36,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牺牲的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.77,0:01:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只能奋起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.14,0:01:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻壳机动队 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.39,0:01:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟这个男人一起拍照有这么快乐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.56,0:01:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家的表情都很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.23,0:01:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他正如其名是难民的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.50,0:01:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本我们这边不是叫他久世英雄而是叫他“朗”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.77,0:01:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.11,0:02:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有时像“狼”一般无情凶残
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.95,0:02:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有时像晴天般晴“朗”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.35,0:02:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是又像不知何时会到处游荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去踪影的流“浪”汉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.82,0:02:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此难民们这么称呼他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.58,0:02:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,＃17  修好母子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,台湾当局也是到最近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.69,0:02:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才注意到这个男子的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难民跟地方角头达成共识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.79,0:02:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始在马路上走动的时候出现奇怪的传言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.30,0:02:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“有一个能领导难民像是指导者一般的男子”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.73,0:02:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚开始只是这样的传言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不久之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难民们开始频频犯下走私案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.84,0:03:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且出现跟地方角头之间有组织的抗争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.08,0:03:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逼着我们有必要去调查那个传言的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于是确认了久世的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.19,0:03:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚开始还以为这样很好\N至少难民不会惹是生非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果却大伤脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.46,0:03:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们到最近为止还不过是船民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在却不论在与陆地的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或是跟角头之间的抗争方式上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.74,0:03:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都一口气升级了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这一切的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都在这个男人身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我不得不承认他是一个了不起的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.01,0:03:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,C4塑胶炸弹的走私管道也是他建立的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.72,0:03:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用改装渔船来做海盗行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经是难民的拿手好戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽管如此  对我们来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.59,0:03:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“朗”愿意自行离开台湾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是帮了我们一个大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  对日本公安就得表示哀悼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世离开这里的理由为何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据那些人所说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.01,0:04:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他为了保养义体不得不回日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  是真是假没人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切合情合理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你  很有参考价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.69,0:04:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于你回程的机票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.03,0:04:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不巧今天没有航班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改明天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.53,0:04:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如你知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.17,0:04:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟大陆的邦交好不容易开始正常化却出现日美安保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.71,0:04:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火星飞得到的范围内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.54,0:04:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,常发生有火药味的事件乃是世上的常态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.31,0:04:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,国际线的航班管理也因此无法照原定班表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.22,0:04:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以替繁忙的公安职员挤出休息的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一天就去观光一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.23,0:05:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.60,0:05:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你不要一个人跑到难民街去闲逛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.23,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这条街已经没有更多情报了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.27,0:05:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果想调查的话  要往西去大陆旅行看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在各地的难民街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.24,0:05:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,据说到现在还是四处都有欢迎那家伙的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.15,0:05:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.28,0:05:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他实际上并没有被全世界通缉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该不会有人去确认这件事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.67,0:05:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.43,0:05:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出现在长崎的中枢电脑  我想多半就是久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.37,0:05:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是以这边的难民来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.87,0:05:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多老人和小孩都没有电子脑化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.34,0:05:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此  他是如何让他们跟自己的思考同步呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我在这里工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.19,0:06:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是我们的交换条件吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对小孩子也毫不留情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把偷来的东西物归原主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不叫作交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说  东西在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.44,0:06:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,东西在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.75,0:06:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.26,0:06:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.19,0:07:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你负责到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.59,0:07:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,负责？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.53,0:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那群人叫作“小杰帮”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.40,0:07:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这附近的新兴帮派角头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做了那种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.14,0:07:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们不是会回来做更严厉的报复吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明不是我做的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道说我静静地看你的手被砍下来比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从某个角度来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你就去道歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.28,0:07:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次光一只手可能解决不了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.76,0:07:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这是在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算恩将仇报吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.04,0:08:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姐姐难道是全身义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.75,0:08:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我第一次看到这种高级货
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.82,0:08:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你从哪里来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.25,0:08:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我决定以后要像“朗”那样换成全身义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.82,0:08:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不过是少一条手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本不觉得怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.09,0:08:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“朗”？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认识“朗”？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问问题的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.46,0:08:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底想干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.93,0:08:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是想请你负责到底而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.64,0:08:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.44,0:08:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  快点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.94,0:08:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.78,0:08:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.07,0:09:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.84,0:09:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,模型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.91,0:09:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那边是绝种动物EX系列的青海龟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.64,0:09:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边是EW系列的鸵鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得很不错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.75,0:09:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再来就等上色之后出货了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是大战前制作的真品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟真品比较起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管怎么做  涂色上总有点粗糙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.16,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小地方的细节也会被涂坏掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.83,0:09:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  上面有刻印和型号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起来几乎就像真品不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.67,0:09:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不懂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.87,0:09:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.17,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这全都是可卡因做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用压力成型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说是以前墨西哥一带常用的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.65,0:09:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是这种模型  就算大人带着也不奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想出来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.22,0:10:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是“朗”想出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然这是第一次实际进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.33,0:10:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这么做是想让我分享重大秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.63,0:10:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,硬拉我进来当同伙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.47,0:10:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姐姐不可能是“小杰”或“黄龙”的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.48,0:10:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是既不是难民也不是普通的旅客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.81,0:10:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要弄到全身义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.88,0:10:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你说不定知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.95,0:10:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非法弄到那种义体的渠道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.26,0:10:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你弄到全身义体想做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想继承“朗”想做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什么嘛  这种时候打来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊  多谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.40,0:10:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会躲到某个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们也消失一阵子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.74,0:10:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.98,0:10:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些家伙都是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.41,0:10:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会注意到这是什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.02,0:11:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小杰帮那些人好像找到这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.76,0:11:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我想像中更气派呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.49,0:11:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  为什么到这种地方来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.13,0:11:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去我藏身的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里比那种地方安全多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我顶楼的套房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,套房吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白金卡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.02,0:12:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姐姐你到底是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.07,0:12:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们家的教育方针就是不让小孩叫我妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.37,0:12:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我妈妈很年轻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚跟日本进行的会谈当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.35,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日美安保缔结后的美军驻军问题成为焦点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.79,0:12:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日方的回应…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.29,0:12:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然现在鸵鸟只饲养来食用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.09,0:12:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过到本世纪初为止  它们还像这样奔驰在草原上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了保护小鸟不受天敌伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.83,0:12:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,族群中最强的母鸟会收养所有的小鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.87,0:13:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你接下来打算怎么办\N把别的小鸟放在自己的小鸟旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.57,0:13:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借此留下最强的基因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.81,0:13:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被期待太多我会很伤脑筋  所以把话说在前头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明天早上就要离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.89,0:13:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会害你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.59,0:13:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去跟警察说明清楚  请他们保护你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.63,0:13:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁会保护一个难民的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难民在这世界上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管哪里都没有容身之处不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.40,0:13:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不过是给你们资产阶级吃的鸵鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.48,0:13:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“朗”这么教你的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.15,0:13:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在这里是什么样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.98,0:13:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既是英雄也是神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他建议你义体化的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.76,0:13:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.99,0:13:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  要做跟“朗”一样的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也必须义体化才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.26,0:13:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是年轻莽撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.70,0:14:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“朗”说他自己在很久以前就已经死过一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.10,0:14:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以剩下的灵魂之火要替理解自己的人燃烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.11,0:14:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对一切绝望的我来说  这句话仿佛给了我希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是复制品也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.31,0:14:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个人有全部模仿的价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.65,0:14:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像连电子脑化都没做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.22,0:14:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么跟他的思考同步化的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简单啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要跟“朗”说话就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.73,0:14:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要跟他谈过一次  大家都会喜欢上“朗”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.63,0:14:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是奇特的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.87,0:14:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最初见到你的时候  觉得你跟“朗”很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.57,0:14:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才会找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.98,0:14:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要一个人做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“朗”也都是一个人战斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.55,0:14:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随你高兴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.92,0:14:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.49,0:14:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.57,0:15:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.88,0:15:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以问你一个问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.71,0:15:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全身义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以做爱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想试试看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是不要好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.78,0:15:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ID卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.02,0:16:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车子来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.55,0:16:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.92,0:16:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.79,0:16:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请开到机场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到那家伙挺有骨气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对久世的形象也了解了一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.68,0:17:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正吸引他们的因素是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.55,0:17:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这也是Stand Alone Complex的一种吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赶得上飞机吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.45,0:17:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对来得及的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.66,0:17:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.17,0:17:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本还是个爱撒娇的小鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.87,0:17:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司机先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以载我去这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起一件急事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.34,0:17:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次的交易用普通方法行不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.22,0:17:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我一个人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.02,0:17:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  如果我没有回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.72,0:17:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们之中要有人接下这个计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照“朗”教我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以白白牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.56,0:17:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.03,0:17:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦让我搜查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.13,0:18:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到我还残留着这样的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人带来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是查？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.73,0:18:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.96,0:19:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感谢您愿意听我冒昧的请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.57,0:19:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦  很有礼貌嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕竟初次跟您见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.84,0:19:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上以后将会是共同促进生意成功的伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.68,0:19:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们可还没决定见你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  真是个有趣的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办呢  老板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.32,0:19:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是用这种方式见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.85,0:19:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许有可能成为伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.59,0:19:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不认为吗  小杰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.89,0:19:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老板  您在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.03,0:19:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事我们从一开始就没有想跟黄龙会起冲突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就先杀了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再把同伙的小鬼们也宰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后再来找东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种时间我不记得有叫女人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.59,0:20:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不记得你们有叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老板  打扰您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能让难民的血玷污这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.71,0:20:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这份人情我有一天会用别的方式还给您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉我来晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始谈交易吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.39,0:20:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是昨天的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想用这个交换这孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.96,0:20:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺便也请你们不要对难民报复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要求就这两项
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.64,0:20:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果接受  我就会乖乖消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.47,0:20:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是不行我就不得不用武力来逼你们答应了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.58,0:20:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少瞧不起人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.18,0:20:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的性子可是很急的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也跟“朗”是同一种人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.76,0:21:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如您所看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.77,0:21:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.94,0:21:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.52,0:21:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.78,0:21:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人都会被干掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.46,0:21:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.16,0:21:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要追了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.93,0:21:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知己知彼  百战不殆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.97,0:21:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个交易已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.19,0:22:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“朗”应该没有劝你义体化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.19,0:22:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更没有要你做几乎丧命的危险抗争对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.46,0:22:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有勇气也有才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.10,0:22:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  死了就什么都没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.23,0:22:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要放下自傲，才能创造未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.00,0:22:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.61,0:23:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我体内行星和星星的银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.29,0:23:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听着它们每一个都唱着同样宁静的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.83,0:23:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在现实当中从来没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.83,0:23:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的美丽事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.10,0:23:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有一点怀疑或恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.60,0:23:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到一个声音—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.84,0:23:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字—然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.31,0:23:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省视自身—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.11,0:23:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光随时都围绕着我—时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.65,0:23:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相  所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.99,0:23:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去让这一切成真的—它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.06,0:24:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在躯壳里的美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.26,0:24:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到一个声音—醒来吧
